--------

     	$ gtags
     	$ htags
     	$ global -x main
     	main              82 ctags.c          main(argc, argv)
     	$ mozilla &
     	$ gozilla +82 ctags.c
     	$ gozilla -d main

     	$ firefox &
     	$ gozilla -b firefox +82 ctags.c

DIAGNOSTICS
-----------

Gozilla exits with a non-0 value if an error occurred, 0 otherwise.

